Description: PyQt6 port of the ksnip screenshot and annotation tool
 A Debian package for the PyQt6 port of ksnip located in ksnip_py/.
 It provides screenshot capture, annotation tools, inline text editing,
 and system hunspell-backed spell checking for text annotations.
